Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:02.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The part...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's responding...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time... has begun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The eternal midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:25.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a fine job, Kanaloa. \NNow rest for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! The octopus shrank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Down to bite-size... It looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time Has Begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nullified?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So magic doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nullified, my ass! That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't beat him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Goat, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can nullify all forms of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no different than \Nwhen we were in Edolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I scrap with Gray all year \N'round, so I'm used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dream, even Titania \Nconfessed her love for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He even cancelled my ability to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured it wouldn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}figured{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I nullify {\i1}everything{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you listen when someone's talking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't use magic, we can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! How are you gonna attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought of somethin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:13.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first split up, Gildarts \Nwas using magic, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I beat him without magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be like I beat Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For better or worse, you are positive, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I told you that the \Nfate of the world is at stake,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all you care about is winning \Nor losing for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weight that we bear on our \Nshoulders is different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to throw away our \Nlives for the sake of our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back to that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our enemy, but he's got guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight is just about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! This is totally hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Salamander and you brats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:05:00.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm just lookin' forward to a \Ntotally hot battle with you doin' your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:09.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fainted from anemia. You \Njust need to rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has something to do with the \Nmagic spell I was under, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I try, I can't remember \Nany of the time when I was a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...what will happen to me if I {\i1}do{\i0} remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I be able to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were turned into a snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't remember \Nanything from then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remember one thing, that \Nmy friend made me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That even if we were separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:49.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he would ride a shooting star \Nto come and get me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the snake that was \Nhanging around before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:06:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The snake showed signs of \Nbeing put under a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you lifted the curse, \Nit was really a girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except it was a powerful spell, and \NI couldn't detect its purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, her condition is unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So if she remembers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:16.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I took her in, so \Nwe can keep an eye on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meddling old man! Yeesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice that only she can hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With apologies to Kinana, when her \Nmemories of being a snake do return,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it may not be something to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So her memories may prove poisonous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll all watch over her, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse, shmurse! You've got \Nnothin' to worry about now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause no matter what \Nhappens, we'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So just hush up and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:58.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:08.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepared to throw your lives \Naway for some duty, ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:14.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lives aren't meant to be \Ntossed away like garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fightin' because of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And 'cause of our bond, \Nwe can overcome anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:26.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends ain't some tools that you use!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And they ain't somethin' \Nyou can just throw away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what life's about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many hits has he taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait... wait and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:45.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes don't look \Nanywhere close to giving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Don't even think \Nof gettin' in on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} takin' this guy down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Fairy Tail wizard, \NI swear I'll take him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, he can't even stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Natsu won't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure... he'll look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's the enemy, kudos to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan-san, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:19.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...really Zentopia's enemy? {\i1}Our{\i0} enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:20.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that hideous face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A weak blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:38.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at you, a feeling \Nlong forgotten comes to the fore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fury?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"For your friend", "life"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you seem to speak sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, you people are guild wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You lot take on jobs for the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so for you to mock our noble \Nmission... It's preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! Who does it for the money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rent...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Food expenses...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, tell him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd hit \Nthe nail on the head...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still talkin' nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, you bastards \Nare the ones who stole from Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without the Infinity Clock in operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,chaos is already loose in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...to minimize its influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:32.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentopia teaches us to display proper \Nbehavior even as we monitor the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:37.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning that path into action \Nis the duty of Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Then you're clueless, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's suddenly full of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crypt candles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:56.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate the sacred flames of the \Ncrypt?! How blasphemous can you get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were gonna \Nkeep preachin', Octo-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although that kinda talk just goes \Nin one ear and out the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that stuck is "friend" and "lives".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'm gonna pay you back \N100-fold for insulting the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's provoking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he doesn't need to go to \Nthe trouble of making him angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Natsu for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end is in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end is in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end is in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is His Grace's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though the birthday \Nevent is about to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we assemble the cardinals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To elect the next archbishop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:56.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Rapowant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak of foolishness such \Nas replacing the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Realize that we are facing \Na much bigger problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a traitor within Zentopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He tarnishes our history,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,spills information about \Nthe Infinity Clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks on the provincial diocese...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it was abetted \Nby someone on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have a reason to lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suspicious of the priest who \Nsurvived the attack that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to question him \Ndirectly. Bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look after the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, no one shall enter his bedchamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrieving the Infinity Clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Legion's holy mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild's principles can't compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make magic by eating \Nfire, I can nullify that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro-sama has never used attacking magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco, I think you already know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Byro-sama's combat technique
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is among the five strongest in all of Fiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:31.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weak have no right to control this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:39.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People can't survive without \Nsomething to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:48.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Zentopia. It's only \Nnatural to depend on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, if His Grace tells us to search \Nfor the clock, we'll look until we find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if being scrupulous about the methods \Nmeans not being able to find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that's our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I, but you're definitely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you thought about all the people who \Nare going to suffer because of your mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:15.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's foolish to act upon your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To provide the correct path and \Nto follow the correct path,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we are forced to make hard choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is always full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the sense to know that at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, it's natural that at the end of \Nthe path I choose, there will be sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:40.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. The cryptex in my \Nhead got all scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make hard choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it must be easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't decide by emotions, but \Nby following your cause, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't prick your conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone could easily make \Nthose choices, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you explain \Nwhat everyone's talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-pi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you contest the whole \Nconcept of a rightful cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of rightful cause \Nmakes people sad and suffer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In Edolas, we saw a lot of people suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Exceeds going through hardships!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:25.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A path that forces you to cause people \Npain and sacrifice them along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is one that'll eventually \Nfall to pieces and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:31.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the way you want everyone to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a fish is free to swim wherever \Nit wants in the water, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We take requests from people who \Nare in trouble and help them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so they can be happy and we get a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we've been operating all \Nalong. That's what a guild does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Against you and that fake righteousness \Nyou hold over your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail isn't gonna be beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake righteousness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Your ridicule of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, your ridicule of \NZentopia knows no bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rightful cause, my butt! \NYou should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy... Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Our guild isn't built on logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We act to protect our honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You spout nonsense! And for that you \Nshall receive Heaven's punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:20.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That glow... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he uses that against people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:33.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn in the flames of your \Nown sins... and be purified!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:45.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It missed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a 0, Byro-sama! Please, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The path of righteousness for \NLegion... for all Zentopia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...just can't be for the \Npurpose of hurting people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the righteous path the one \Nwhere we guide the powerless lambs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going down the path that sacrifices people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer accept that contradiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you turn your back on the faith?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what my fate will \Nbe for betraying Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see what lies at the \Nend of our righteous path anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Righteousness is a straight arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:36.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It pierces everything, leading \Nto the truth in a straight line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you haven't forgotten that precept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that arrow sacrifices many \Npowerless lambs along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then it should be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our doctrine isn't everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching what these people do touched me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so nice and look like \Nthey have so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll feel it too, Byro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you face these people with your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been poisoned?! You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't even wait for the hearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be judged right here, Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...really did want to become your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, we didn't have \Na chance to cross swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we finally meet, Byro Cracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Titania" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming an attack at your \Ncomrade in a fit of rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't bully the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why Lyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a hunch there was trouble, \Nso we hustled on over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And look what we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight was just \Nabout to start and then you waltz in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:19.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! You all found \Nthe parts of the clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel is here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla's team found a part, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, everyone! There's the one we found!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we've obtained all five parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:35.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is the clock \Nhand you people stole from Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, come and get it, Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stand against all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to seal away all the parts \Nof the clock and keep them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So just give that to me without protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Infinity Clock originally \Nbelonged to Zentopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bound to take charge of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This is the first I've heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You peered at the darkness \Nthat mustn't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Already, I cannot allow \Nyou to leave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Balderdash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, wait! Magic doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:36.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what that guy was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even against our numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic doesn't work on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew he was {\i1}this{\i0} strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure, this is a pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:45.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Now it's like I'm just a normal cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many of you attack \Nat once, it makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Against me, wizards are no longer wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's nothing for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to beat the crap \Nout of you with our bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in a physical fight, I'm trained \Nto take on 50 people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're fired up too, huh, Octo-man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. He's a master \Nof the fighting arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said... not to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time was etched, and then chaos descended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:40.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the beginning of the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... This miasma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san! Look! The clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?! It's ringing in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My head feels like it's splitting in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:30.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilgrims!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're closing in at the foot of the slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't open the gate yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At least protect His Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it... the eternal midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:49.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The maggots...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're swarming...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn thing's noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:56.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an alarm clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The crypt will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:21:59.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's not just stand \Naround! We gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:10.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're{\i0} here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:58.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The clock's started to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And is that Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That one guy isn't here! The \None with the squarish face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the one that goes, "...yes", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's the one. But you \Ndidn't sound like him one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Says you... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.51,0:24:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The New Oracion Seis Appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sound like him, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.46,0:24:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sound just like him, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:21.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you do! Totally like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't give up!
